abstract: The company has filed a proposal with the Hong Kong Stock Exchange to list its Web hosting unit, HiChina.
snippet: The company has filed a proposal with the Hong Kong Stock Exchange to list its Web hosting unit, HiChina.
lead_paragraph: Alibaba.com announced on Monday that it was readying its Web hosting unit, HiChina, for a potential public offering.

headline.main: Alibaba to Spin Off a Unit
